*****************************************************************************

hp3d - A Scalable MPI/OpenMP hp-Adaptive Finite Element Software Library
       for Complex Multiphysics Applications

1. Build instructions: see README

2. Compatibility with required external libraries:

 - PETSc
   Versions: 3.11 - 3.15

 - HDF5
   Versions: 1.10.4 - 1.12.1

 - MUMPS
   Versions: 5.1 - 5.5.1

 - METIS
   Versions: 5.1.0
   
 - ParMETIS
   Versions: 4.0.3

 - PT-Scotch
   (requires bison version >= 3.0)
   Versions: 6.0.9
             7.0.1

 - Zoltan
   Versions: 3.83

*****************************************************************************
